 CreateRegistry←{
⍝ Creates a brand new APM registry.\\
⍝ `⍵` must either not exist or be an empty folder.\\
⍝ An empty file `index.json` is injected and a sub folder `packages` created.
     path←⍵
     rc←3 ⎕MKDIR path
     files←⊃⎕NINFO⍠1⊢path,'/*'
     0≠≢files:1 'Path provided must be empty'
     rc←(⊂'[]')⎕NPUT path,'/index.json'
     rc←3 ⎕MKDIR path,'/packages'
     0 ''
 }
